penguins %>%
  group_by(species) %>%
  summarise(billmean = mean(bill_length_mm, na.rm = TRUE)) %>%
  kbl() %>% # make it a kable table
  kable_classic()%>% 
  row_spec(2, bold = T, color = "white", background = "red") %>%
  kable_styling(full_width = FALSE)
